---
export const prerender = true;
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Terms of Use — ActivityRadar"
  description="Terms of use for ActivityRadar."
>
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-14">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-navy mb-8">Terms of Use</h1>

    <div class="text-navy/80 leading-relaxed flex flex-col gap-6">

      <section>
        <p>
          ActivityRadar is a directory of youth activity organizations in the Puget Sound region,
          published by Field &amp; Forge Ventures. The directory is information, not professional
          advice. Nothing here replaces your own judgment about whether a program fits your child.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-navy text-base mb-3">The directory</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">
          Organization records come from public sources (IRS data, organization websites, and
          user submissions). We review submissions before publishing them. We work to keep
          information accurate, but we cannot guarantee that every listing is complete or current.
          Registration links and contact details belong to the organizations and change on their
          own schedules. Always confirm details directly with an organization before signing up.
        </p>
        <p>
          Registration happens directly between you and the organization. ActivityRadar is not
          a party to that transaction.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-navy text-base mb-3">Claiming a listing</h2>
        <p>
          If you submit a claim request, you represent that you are authorized to act on behalf
          of that organization. We review every claim before approving it. Approved listings may
          be edited by the claimant; we reserve the right to remove any listing that contains
          inaccurate or misleading information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-navy text-base mb-3">Search data</h2>
        <p>
          When you search, we log the query and result count to understand where the directory
          has gaps. We do not log your identity, IP address, or link searches to you as an
          individual. See our <a href="/privacy" class="text-rust hover:underline">privacy page</a>
          for details.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-navy text-base mb-3">No warranties, limited liability</h2>
        <p>
          The site is provided as-is. To the fullest extent the law allows, ActivityRadar and
          Field &amp; Forge Ventures are not liable for damages arising from your use of the site
          or from any transaction with an organization listed here.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-navy text-base mb-3">Governing law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Washington, USA.
          We may update them; the date below tells you when. If we change something material,
          we will say so plainly.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-navy/70">Last updated: June 2026</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-semibold text-navy text-base mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          ActivityRadar is published by Field &amp; Forge Ventures.
          Questions: <a href="mailto:jeffthomas@pugetsound.edu" class="text-rust hover:underline">jeffthomas@pugetsound.edu</a>.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
